text: Truly useful tip! No wonder since the Circuit Breaker I also, may similar to some people, feel so depressed and feeling locked, but when I found something passionate that can do it at home, even though depression may not gone away instantly, but it will help us to distract our mind, finding joy and peace from what we like to do and we will see that the more peace we got, the more traces of depression will gone one step at a time. 😊 Standing with those who may have been through tough times during the Circuit Breaker, you are an overcomer stand strong, and let's fight against the depression with our hope and faith from the inner side! #sgunited
